review_title: Skeptical at first but this really works even at half dosage
review_text:
This is one of the few brands that uses soft gelatin capsules which are non-toxic and easy to digest, unlike 'vegan' capsules. 

As for the quality of the 5HTP - the number one thing I noticed was that I automatically get VERY sleepy when it's time for bed - which is a good thing! I think this has something to do with the body having more 'material' to make melatonin. 

Second thing I noticed is I needed way less sleep and my body tends to wake up automatically without an alarm clock, though usually way earlier than intended. Needless to say, the sleep was actually more restful with this stuff than without. Additionally, I was also more awake during the day, even the post-lunch food coma is no longer a thing. Don't even need coffee anymore!

Last significant thing I noticed was significantly less cravings and hangry bouts - I basically eat less, and eat less often. I would say I would need to eat around less than half the amount I usually do everyday. I can skip meals (like dinner) and still comfortably go to bed due to how sleepy it makes me at night (even though I take two during the day instead of at night, and at midday only, meaning half dosage).
